message: Hi Bhakti
This is Awkward but bear with me😅

I have been thinking about us 🙈

 I know you always said
Marriage😱 scares the fuck outta me !!!
And my married friends always said
Run, You fools!🤣
So, I always Brushed it off😗....
Bitch Please, marriage is not for me😋
But one day i realized
Nobody makes me happy like you do🥰

But nobody ever made me feel like that before so my brain said 

 impossible!😣

And realized that i do want to grow old with you , 
 So my heart asked my Brain🙄
If you like it, why u not put ring💍 on it
So i thought about it...🤔
Like a Boss😎
So Bhakti, i crazy bell...😜
I proposed you again on your birthday🤗
Will you...🤨
Will you marry me ?❤️

Ask Bhakti to marry me, 

 She said yes💘
